messages.zh: 灾势减弱了——不，中心转移了！
messages.tl: The disaster has weakened - no, the center has shifted!

messages.zh: 风暴眼不在我们所处的城区，还来得及！
messages.tl: The storm eye is not in the urban area we are in, but it is too late!
Be careful with the pieces! fast! Don't stop!

messages.zh: 前方就是建筑密集区了！灾害中心区域在我们身后！我们完全能——
messages.tl: The front is a densely built area! The disaster center area is behind us! We can do it all -
...Reunion Movement... Is there so many people...

messages.zh: 别停下！在开阔地带停下等于找死！到目的地之后再整顿队形！
messages.tl: Don't stop! Stopping in an open area is like finding death! Reorganize the formation after arriving at the destination!

messages.zh: （二八开。希望渺茫，但能行。只是......）
messages.tl: (Two eight open. Hope, but can do. Just...)
How can it be! Where are they from...?

messages.zh: 这个数量......整合运动很看得起我们啊。
messages.tl: This number... The Reunion Movement is very good for us.

messages.zh: 别轻举妄动！她是资料上整合运动的领袖之一......
messages.tl: Don't act rashly! She is one of the leaders of the Reunion Movement on the data...

messages.zh: 不，现在看来她就是真正的领袖——
messages.tl: No, now she seems to be the real leader -
The tyrant of the Reunion Movement, huh -
I have a very bad feeling.
